1
00:00:01,890 --> 00:00:03,450
<i>Hast...</i>

2
00:00:03,450 --> 00:00:06,470
thou not gone against sincerity?

3
00:00:06,470 --> 00:00:10,300
Hast thou not felt ashamed of thy words and deeds?

4
00:00:10,300 --> 00:00:14,760
Hast thou not become slothful?

5
00:00:15,480 --> 00:00:20,120
I shall continue to adhere to and uphold these venerated principles.

6
00:00:24,050 --> 00:00:26,950
- Good morning.
- Morning.

7
00:00:26,950 --> 00:00:28,460
I'm sorry, I overslept.

8
00:00:28,460 --> 00:00:30,020
No worries.

9
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:33,460
From now onward, we are not husband and wife.

10
00:00:33,460 --> 00:00:37,120
Rather, let us cohabit as acquaintances.

11
00:00:37,780 --> 00:00:41,720
Wake up whenever you'd like. I will recite my house rules alone.

12
00:00:41,720 --> 00:00:46,750
Meal prep and chores shall be done by none other than ourselves.

13
00:00:46,750 --> 00:00:48,780
There's no need to match the other's pace.

14
00:00:48,780 --> 00:00:52,940
All great ideas, since we're getting a divorce.

15
00:00:52,940 --> 00:00:56,420
<i>I guess you and I will have to get divorced, after all.
</i>

16
00:00:56,420 --> 00:00:58,280
<i>That's right.</i>

17
00:00:58,280 --> 00:01:03,030
<i>I think that's the best choice for both of us.</i>

18
00:01:06,870 --> 00:01:09,400
I shall go for a run.

19
00:01:11,990 --> 00:01:19,990
<i>Timing and Subtitles brought to you by
